---
import Industrial3D from "./Industrial3D.jsx";
---
<section class="sec sec-3d" id="innovation">
  <div class="wrap grid-3d">
    <div class="content-3d">
      <div class="label-pill">Tecnología V4</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Ingeniería Web de <span class="grad-text">Alto Impacto</span></h2>
      <p class="sec-sub">
        Nuestros sistemas no son solo visuales. Se construyen con la misma precisión
        que una planta siderúrgica, optimizando cada byte para una carga instantánea
        que impulsa tus conversiones.
      </p>
      <ul class="feat-3d-list">
        <li><strong>Arquitectura de Islas:</strong> Interactividad selectiva para 0ms de bloqueo de CPU.</li>
        <li><strong>Shader Engine:</strong> Efectos visuales de élite que no penalizan el SEO.</li>
        <li><strong>Data-Driven Design:</strong> Decisiones de diseño basadas en telemetría real.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="visual-3d">
      <Industrial3D client:visible />
      <div class="status-overlay">
        <div class="status-dot"></div>
        <span>Sístema Operativo V2 (Online)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sec-3d {
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05), transparent 50%);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 120px 0;
  }

  .grid-3d {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .feat-3d-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feat-3d-list li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .feat-3d-list li strong {
    color: var(--safety-orange);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .visual-3d {
    position: relative;
    height: 600px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
    border-radius: 40px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .status-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 30px;
    left: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #22c55e;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #22c55e;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .grid-3d { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4rem; }
    .content-3d { text-align: center; }
    .feat-3d-list { align-items: center; }
    .visual-3d { height: 450px; }
  }
</style>
